## 构建与测试命令

### Go 服务
```bash
cd inv_api_server && go build -o inv-api-server ./cmd/main.go
cd inv_api_server && go test ./... -v
cd inv_api_server && go vet ./...
cd inv_device_server && go build -o inv-device-server ./cmd/main.go
cd api-gateway && go build -o api-gateway ./main.go
cd mqtt-kafka-bridge && go build -o mqtt-kafka-bridge ./main.go
```

### Docker
```bash
cd deploy && docker compose build inv-api-server inv-device-server
cd deploy && docker compose up -d
cd deploy && docker compose logs -f inv-api-server
```

### Flutter App
```bash
cd inv_app && flutter pub get
cd inv_app && flutter analyze
cd inv_app && flutter test
cd inv_app && flutter build apk --release
cd inv_app && flutter run
```

### React 管理后台
```bash
cd inv-admin-frontend && npm install
cd inv-admin-frontend && npm run dev
cd inv-admin-frontend && npm run build
cd inv-admin-frontend && npx tsc --noEmit
```

